_:N9ec0e308cc7e4e9194420aae3d6195f4 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Simon has extensive experience of complex procurement programmes and change leadership from senior government roles at the Ministry of Defence.</p>\n\n<p>Operating at board level, Simon has led serial improvements in the naval procurement and support sector, through organisational and cultural change, commercial renegotiation and supply chain performance management.</p>\n\n<p>He’s a graduate of the Sloan Fellowship, a Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering, and a graduate of the Major Projects Leadership Academy.</p>\n\n<p>Simon stepped down from the Office for Nuclear Regulation’s (ONR) board in November 2022, after four and a half years as a Non-Executive Director, to take up a role on the Board as a Non-Executive Director at Sellafield Ltd.</p>\n\n" .
